summary: Falskaar compatibility patch for Open Faced Helmets by MadCat221
descriptionHtml:
Just a small patch to make Open Faced Helmets by MadCat221 (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4866/) compatible with Falskaar. Original mod is still necessary. The modified ESP is based on Sharlikrans Compatibility Patch for Open Face Helmets (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26230/)

Install after Open Face Helmets V1_3 using NMM

Full credits go to MadCat221 and Sharlikran
author: holmenknollen
